* Capitalcall and Citytime peak-rate call charges are 20 pence a minute
for calls made from within the M25 orbital motorway, and 50 pence a
minute for calls from elsewhere. In both cases, off-peak calls cost 10
pence a minute.
+ MetroDigital peak-rate call charges are 20 pence a minute for local
calls and 25 pence a minute for long-distance calls, provided they are
made from within a MetroDigital coverage area. In both cases, off-peak
calls will cost 10 pence a minute. Calls from outside MetroDigital
coverage areas will cost 50 pence minute at peak times and 10 pence a
minute off-peak.
When calls are made from a subscriber's home cell, peak rate
charges are 10 pence a minute for local calls and 12.5 pence a minute
for long-distance calls. Local and long-distance off-peak calls made
from inside the home cell both cost five pence a minute.
