</XX>
<CO>Cott Corp.
    PepsiCo Inc.
    Coca-Cola Inc.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>CAZ  Canada.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P2086 Bottled and Canned Soft Drinks.
</IN>
<XX>
