accounts for FM4.8bn of the backlog.
Valmet warned that its full-year result would be affected by the
recently-completed FM1.62bn sale of its transport equipment and tractor
operations to Sisu-Auto. The transfer will cut 1994 net sales by 20 per
cent, to around FM8.5bn, and reduce operating income from 1993's FM479m.
